FBIS4-63761 "drsov101_d_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 Regional Affairs Yeltsin Appoints Gladskiy Acting Head of Krasnodar Kray Yeltsin Appoints Gladskiy Acting Head of Krasnodar Kray LD2405152494 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1412 GMT 24 May 94 LD2405152494 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS] [Text] Moscow, 24 May -- Following a representation by the chairman of the Russian Federation Government, Boris Yeltsin issued a decree today appointing Viktor Gladskiy to the post of acting head of the administration of Krasnodar Kray. This has been reported by the Russian Federation president's press service.
